promptTranslations.en:
Minimalism, new Chinese style 3D graphic design, with Chinese kaishu script at the bottom of the image: “Eastern Aesthetics”, “2026/04/18”, signed “CHINA” and “@LIYUE”;
Painted on a smooth matte pure white thick art paper, a creative landscape filled with Eastern poetic atmosphere, featuring an irregular torn paper effect;
The Chinese mythical beast: Qiongqi, depicted fully with exquisite patterns, beautifully elegant and vivid lines, eyes bright and spirited, majestic expression, graceful posture, luxurious decorative art with traditional Chinese motifs;
Fluorescent blue lines, 0.5mm ultra-fine golden metallic outlines, splattered white ink brushstrokes, color rendering, red background, and romantic poetic blues;
A dreamlike scene interweaving warm and cool light, with strong contrasting shadows creating an atmospheric effect, delicate floral dancing time narrative, Zen Eastern wind, large areas of white space, framed composition, white space at the bottom, clear detailed elements.
